    "In our general framework, we consider a system over time t from the start or initial time t I to the end or final time t F with a time horizon of t H = t F -t I, and a model with m latent state variables or stocks represented as a column vector x, n latent static variables or auxiliaries as a column vector y, and p indicators or observed variables as a column vector z with q observations over [t I, t F ] in the observed data matrix or frame O,",
